column5: Binge watching and rewatching right now.  Forgot about this crappie episode, WOW!  Its short back packs in alot of info  Check it out if you're bored
this is the video that got me into uncut...i wasnt even a big crappie guy, but his detail and busting out the vice during the episode...i was like who the hell is this guy.
I love his sense of humour and he sure is knowledgeable!
